d ears / neck\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"headache\", \"label\": \"Headache\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"severe_headache\", \"label\": \"Severe headache\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"stiff_neck\", \"label\": \"Stiff neck / neck rigidity\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"photophobia\", \"label\": \"Sensitivity to light / photophobia\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"altered_consciousness\", \"label\": \"Altered consciousness / confusion\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"seizures\", \"label\": \"Seizures / convulsions\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"paralysis_acute_flaccid\", \"label\": \"Acute flaccid paralysis\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"hydrophobia\", \"label\": \"Hydrophobia (fear of water / unable to swallow)\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"aerophobia\", \"label\": \"Aerophobia (fear of air currents)\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"encephalitis_signs\", \"label\": \"Encephalitis / brain inflammation signs\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"fatigue\", \"label\": \"Fatigue\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"severe_fatigue\", \"label\": \"Severe fatigue / prostration\", \"who_priority\": true}, {\"id\": \"malaise\", \"label\": \"Malaise / generally unwell\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"weakness\", \"label\": \"Weakness\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"anorexia\", \"label\": \"Loss of appetite / anorexia\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"muscle_pain\", \"label\": \"Muscle pain / myalgia\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"calf_muscle_pain\", \"label\": \"Severe calf muscle pain / tenderness\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"joint_pain\", \"label\": \"Joint pain / arthralgia\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"severe_joint_pain\", \"label\": \"Severe / debilitating joint pain\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"back_pain\", \"label\": \"Back pain\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"limb_pain\", \"label\": \"Pain in limbs\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"chest_tightness\", \"label\": \"Chest tightness\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"conjunctivitis\", \"label\": \"Conjunctivitis / red eyes\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"pain_behind_eyes\", \"label\": \"Pain behind the eyes\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"facial_swelling\", \"label\": \"Facial swelling\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"hearing_loss\", \"label\": \"Hearing loss\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"loss_of_taste_smell\", \"label\": \"Loss or change of taste/smell\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"splenomegaly\", \"label\": \"Enlarged spleen / splenomegaly\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"hepatomegaly\", \"label\": \"Enlarged liver / hepatomegaly\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"cold_pale_skin\", \"label\": \"Pale or cold skin / shock signs\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"dizziness\", \"label\": \"Dizziness / vertigo\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"low_energy\", \"label\": \"Low energy\", \"who_priority\": false}, {\"id\": \"weight_loss\", \"label\": \"Unexplained weight loss\", \"who_priority\": false}]','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(6,'diseases.exposure_catalog','window.DISEASES.exposure_catalog from src/Diseases.js','[{\"id\": \"close_contact_case\", \"label\": \"Close contact with symptomatic case\"}, {\"id\": \"contact_body_fluids\", \"label\": \"Direct contact with body fluids\"}, {\"id\": \"contact_dead_body\", \"label\": \"Contact with dead body / funeral exposure\"}, {\"id\": \"funeral_or_burial_exposure\", \"label\": \"Funeral or burial participation\"}, {\"id\": \"healthcare_exposure\", \"label\": \"Healthcare or caregiving exposure\"}, {\"id\": \"travel_from_outbreak_area\", \"label\": \"Travel from outbreak/affected area\"}, {\"id\": \"residence_in_outbreak_area\", \"label\": \"Residence in outbreak/affected area\"}, {\"id\": \"unsafe_water\", \"label\": \"Unsafe water / poor sanitation\"}, {\"id\": \"contaminated_food_or_water\", \"label\": \"Likely contaminated food or water\"}, {\"id\": \"poultry_or_live_bird_exposure\", \"label\": \"Poultry / live bird / bird market exposure\"}, {\"id\": \"camel_exposure_or_mideast_healthcare\", \"label\": \"Camel exposure or recent healthcare in Middle East\"}, {\"id\": \"rodent_exposure\", \"label\": \"Rodent exposure / rodent-contaminated surfaces\"}, {\"id\": \"mosquito_exposure\", \"label\": \"Mosquito exposure in endemic area\"}, {\"id\": \"flood_livestock_exposure\", \"label\": \"Livestock, raw animal tissues, or flood/agricultural outbreak\"}, {\"id\": \"contact_with_rash_case\", \"label\": \"Contact with person with rash illness\"}, {\"id\": \"unvaccinated_or_unknown_vaccination\", \"label\": \"Unvaccinated or vaccination status unknown\"}, {\"id\": \"contact_with_paralysis_case\", \"label\": \"Contact with acute flaccid paralysis case\"}, {\"id\": \"flea_or_rodent_exposure\", \"label\": \"Flea bite / rodent exposure\"}, {\"id\": \"animal_bite_or_wildlife_contact\", \"label\": \"Animal bite, scratch, or wildlife carcass contact\"}, {\"id\": \"sexual_contact\", \"label\": \"Recent sexual contact with symptomatic person\"}, {\"id\": \"laboratory_exposure\", \"label\": \"Laboratory exposure (biosafety incident)\"}, {\"id\": \"affected_healthcare_facility_exposure\", \"label\": \"Exposure to affected healthcare facility or cluster\"}, {\"id\": \"crowded_closed_setting\", \"label\": \"Crowded enclosed setting / respiratory spread risk\"}, {\"id\": \"tick_bite\", \"label\": \"Tick bite or exposure in tick-endemic area\"}, {\"id\": \"raw_meat_or_unpasteurised_dairy\", \"label\": \"Raw meat, blood, or unpasteurised dairy consumption\"}, {\"id\": \"fresh_water_contact\", \"label\": \"Fresh water contact (rivers, flooding, wading)\"}]','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(7,'diseases.priority_tiers','window.DISEASES.priority_tiers from src/Diseases.js','{\"tier_4_syndromic\": \"Important travel-medicine and syndromic differential\", \"tier_2_ihr_annex2\": \"IHR Tier 2 — Annex 2 epidemic-prone disease (four-question decision instrument)\", \"tier_1_ihr_critical\": \"IHR Tier 1 — Always Notifiable (PHEIC by definition regardless of score)\", \"tier_2_ihr_equivalent\": \"IHR-equivalent WHO AFRO Priority 1 disease\", \"tier_3_who_notifiable\": \"WHO notifiable / national reporting required\"}','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(8,'diseases.syndrome_rules','window.DISEASES.syndrome_rules from src/Diseases.js','[{\"any\": [\"bleeding\", \"bleeding_gums_or_nose\", \"bloody_sputum\", \"petechial_or_purpuric_rash\", \"bruising_or_ecchymosis\", \"hematuria\", \"blood_in_vomit\"], \"priority\": 1, \"syndrome\": \"VHF\", \"reasoning\": \"Hemorrhagic manifestation detected. VHF protocol must be activated.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\", \"sudden_onset_fever\", \"very_high_fever\"], \"priority\": 2, \"requires\": [\"stiff_neck\"], \"syndrome\": \"MENINGITIS\", \"reasoning\": \"Fever with nuchal rigidity fulfills WHO meningitis syndrome case definition.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\"], \"priority\": 3, \"syndrome\": \"MENINGITIS\", \"reasoning\": \"Fever with neurological signs — meningitis/encephalitis must be excluded.\", \"confidence\": \"MEDIUM\", \"requires_any_extra\": [\"altered_consciousness\", \"photophobia\", \"seizures\", \"bulging_fontanelle\"]}, {\"any\": [\"hydrophobia\", \"aerophobia\"], \"priority\": 4, \"syndrome\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"reasoning\": \"Hydrophobia or aerophobia — pathognomonic for rabies. EMERGENCY protocol.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"paralysis_acute_flaccid\"], \"priority\": 5, \"syndrome\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"reasoning\": \"Acute flaccid paralysis — AFP protocol required (polio exclusion mandatory).\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"altered_consciousness\", \"seizures\", \"encephalitis_signs\"], \"priority\": 6, \"syndrome\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"reasoning\": \"Altered consciousness or seizures indicate neurological involvement.\", \"confidence\": \"MEDIUM\"}, {\"any\": [\"bloody_diarrhea\"], \"priority\": 7, \"syndrome\": \"BLOODY_DIARRHEA\", \"reasoning\": \"Bloody diarrhoea meets WHO Bloody Diarrhoea syndrome definition.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\", \"very_high_fever\", \"sudden_onset_fever\"], \"priority\": 8, \"syndrome\": \"SARI\", \"reasoning\": \"Fever with respiratory distress meets WHO SARI case definition.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\", \"requires_any2\": [\"shortness_of_breath\", \"difficulty_breathing\", \"rapid_breathing\", \"oxygen_saturation_low\", \"respiratory_failure_signs\"]}, {\"any\": [\"jaundice\"], \"priority\": 9, \"syndrome\": \"JAUNDICE\", \"reasoning\": \"Clinical jaundice (yellow sclera/skin) — acute jaundice syndrome.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"dark_urine\", \"hepatomegaly\"], \"priority\": 10, \"syndrome\": \"JAUNDICE\", \"reasoning\": \"Dark urine or hepatomegaly may indicate hepatic involvement.\", \"confidence\": \"MEDIUM\"}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\", \"very_high_fever\"], \"priority\": 11, \"syndrome\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"reasoning\": \"Fever with rash meets WHO Febrile Rash Illness syndrome criteria.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\", \"requires_any2\": [\"rash_maculopapular\", \"rash_vesicular_pustular\", \"rash_face_first\", \"painful_rash\", \"skin_eschar\", \"mucosal_lesions\", \"genital_lesions\"]}, {\"any\": [\"rice_water_diarrhea\", \"watery_diarrhea\"], \"priority\": 12, \"syndrome\": \"AWD\", \"reasoning\": \"Profuse watery diarrhoea — Acute Watery Diarrhoea syndrome. Exclude cholera.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\"}, {\"any\": [\"diarrhea\", \"vomiting\"], \"priority\": 13, \"requires\": [\"severe_dehydration\"], \"syndrome\": \"AWD\", \"reasoning\": \"Diarrhoea with severe dehydration — treat as AWD until proven otherwise.\", \"confidence\": \"MEDIUM\"}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\", \"low_grade_fever\", \"sudden_onset_fever\"], \"priority\": 14, \"syndrome\": \"ILI\", \"reasoning\": \"Fever with respiratory symptoms — Influenza-Like Illness syndrome.\", \"confidence\": \"HIGH\", \"requires_any2\": [\"cough\", \"dry_cough\", \"sore_throat\", \"coryza\", \"runny_nose\"]}, {\"any\": [\"fever\", \"high_fever\", \"sudden_onset_fever\", \"very_high_fever\"], \"priority\": 15, \"syndrome\": \"OTHER\", \"reasoning\": \"Undifferentiated febrile illness — needs further clinical workup.\", \"confidence\": \"LOW\"}]','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(9,'diseases.ihr_escalation_rules','window.DISEASES.ihr_escalation_rules from src/Diseases.js','[{\"id\": \"TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL\", \"routing\": \"NATIONAL\", \"reasoning\": \"IHR Article 6: disease that always constitutes PHEIC requires immediate notification.\", \"risk_level\": \"CRITICAL\", \"description\": \"Any IHR Tier 1 disease (always notifiable) in top 3 results at score ≥20\"}, {\"id\": \"VHF_HIGH_CONFIDENCE\", \"routing\": \"NATIONAL\", \"reasoning\": \"High-confidence VHF — IHR Annex 2 mandatory notification pathway.\", \"risk_level\": \"CRITICAL\", \"description\": \"VHF syndrome with high-confidence diagnosis in top 2\"}, {\"id\": \"VHF_POSSIBLE\", \"routing\": \"PHEOC\", \"reasoning\": \"Possible VHF — IHR precautionary isolation pending laboratory confirmation.\", \"risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"description\": \"Any VHF in top 5 with score ≥20\"}, {\"id\": \"SARI_SPO2_CRITICAL\", \"routing\": \"PHEOC\", \"reasoning\": \"SARI with severe hypoxia — potential PHEIC pathogen; immediate respiratory isolation.\", \"risk_level\": \"CRITICAL\", \"description\": \"SARI with SpO2 <90%\"}, {\"id\": \"FEVER_HEMORRHAGE_EMERGENCY\", \"routing\": \"NATIONAL\", \"reasoning\": \"Hemorrhagic fever protocol activated — IHR Annex 2 immediate notification.\", \"risk_level\": \"CRITICAL\", \"description\": \"Emergency signs + hemorrhage\"}, {\"id\": \"BIOTERRORISM_SUSPICION\", \"routing\": \"NATIONAL\", \"reasoning\": \"Bioterrorism indicator — national security protocols apply.\", \"risk_level\": \"CRITICAL\", \"description\": \"Bioterrorism protocol flags (smallpox, anthrax, tularemia cluster)\"}, {\"id\": \"TIER2_HIGH_CONFIDENCE\", \"routing\": \"PHEOC\", \"reasoning\": \"High-confidence IHR Annex 2 disease — PHEOC notification required.\", \"risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"description\": \"IHR Tier 2 Annex 2 disease at score ≥40 in top 1\"}, {\"id\": \"CRITICAL_VITALS\", \"routing\": \"DISTRICT\", \"reasoning\": \"Critical vital signs — immediate medical management required regardless of diagnosis.\", \"risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"description\": \"Life-threatening vital signs regardless of diagnosis\"}, {\"id\": \"AFP_POLIO_RISK\", \"routing\": \"PHEOC\", \"reasoning\": \"AFP detected — IHR Tier 1 (polio) exclusion mandatory. Stool sample collection required.\", \"risk_level\": \"HIGH\", \"description\": \"Acute flaccid paralysis = polio exclusion required\"}]','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(10,'diseases.engine_to_who_syndrome','window.DISEASES.engine_to_who_syndrome from src/Diseases.js','{\"vhf\": \"VHF\", \"plague\": \"OTHER\", \"zoonotic\": \"OTHER\", \"arboviral\": \"OTHER\", \"meningitis\": \"MENINGITIS\", \"neurologic\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"bioterrorism\": \"OTHER\", \"encephalitic\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"encephalitis\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"febrile_rash\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"travel_fever\": \"OTHER\", \"vector_borne\": \"OTHER\", \"acute_febrile\": \"OTHER\", \"renal_failure\": \"OTHER\", \"jaundice_renal\": \"JAUNDICE\", \"shock_syndrome\": \"OTHER\", \"systemic_viral\": \"OTHER\", \"cutaneous_eschar\": \"OTHER\", \"respiratory_rash\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"acute_respiratory\": \"ILI\", \"jaundice_syndrome\": \"JAUNDICE\", \"mild_febrile_rash\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"mild_rash_illness\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"severe_respiratory\": \"SARI\", \"dehydrating_diarrhea\": \"AWD\", \"jaundice_hemorrhagic\": \"VHF\", \"acute_watery_diarrhea\": \"AWD\", \"high_consequence_rash\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"lymphadenitic_febrile\": \"OTHER\", \"vesiculopustular_rash\": \"RASH_FEVER\", \"influenza_like_illness\": \"ILI\", \"neuroinvasive_possible\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"acute_flaccid_paralysis\": \"NEUROLOGICAL\", \"bloody_diarrhea_syndrome\": \"BLOODY_DIARRHEA\", \"chronic_febrile_zoonotic\": \"OTHER\", \"gastrointestinal_systemic\": \"OTHER\", \"gastrointestinal_hemorrhagic\": \"VHF\", \"respiratory_gastrointestinal_mixed\": \"SARI\"}','3.0.0','reference',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13'),(11,'exposures.metadata','window.EXPOSURES.metadata from src/exposures.js','{\"usage\": [\"Call mapToEngineCodes(dbRecords) to translate DB responses to engine codes.\", \"Call getEnhancedScoreResult() in Diseases_intelligence.js passing engine codes.\", \"Never put exposure mapping logic in the Vue — all logic belongs here.\"], \"context\": \"WHO IHR 2005 aligned exposure risk factors for POE secondary screening\", \"version\": \"2.0.0\", \"last_updated\": \"2026-04-01\", \"schema_version\": \"2.0.0\", \"engine_compatibility\": \"Diseases.js v3.0.0+\"}','2.0.0','metadata',1,NULL,NULL,'2026-05-17 15:08:24','2026-05-17 16:09:13');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `ref_engine_config` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

--
-- Table structure for table `ref_exposure_mappings`
--

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `ref_exposure_mappings`;
/*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */;
/*!50503 SET character_set_client = utf8mb4 */;
CREATE TABLE `ref_exposure_mappings` (
  `id` bigint unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `exposure_code` varchar(80) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `engine_code` varchar(80) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `priority` smallint unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `created_by_user_id` bigint unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by_user_id` bigint unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
